<h1>Shatter The Stigma Mend The Mind</h1>

<p>This is an archive of the campaign assets from the Niagara region&rsquo;s <strong>Shatter the Stigma Mend the Mind</strong> mental health anti-stigma campaign. The campaign was spearheaded by <a href="https://www.pathstonementalhealth.ca/">Pathstone Mental Health</a>. This repository is maintained by <a href="https://www.jmr.ca/">JMR Logics</a>.</p>

<p>Visit <a href="https://www.mendthemind.ca/">mendthemind.ca</a></p>

<p>The source for mendthemind.ca can be found at <a href="https://github.com/mendthemind/mendthemind">GitHub</a></p>
